\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

 measures the size of the environmental change and 
\begin_inset Formula $\xi_{t}$
\end_inset

 is Gaussian random noise with mean zero, variance 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{\xi}^{2}$
\end_inset

 and autocorrelation 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

.
 The results are shown in Figs.
