\begin_inset Formula $G_{mm}\bar{a}^{2}$
\end_inset

.
 In consequence, the phenotype remains maladapted in the long term, undershootin
g its target 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 somewhat, and in consequence both the slope of the plastic response 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{b}$
\end_inset

 and the maternal effect coefficient 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{m}$
\end_inset

